data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":390,"item_id":"msg_98266cbfb57f837f00693a04e821788190bb8d0f2ee1caf5c1","output_index":1,"content_index":0,"text":"Contoso offers innovative products under the brand name \"Contoso Galaxy Innovations,\" specifically in the Smart Eyewear category. Here are the detailed features of their product:\n\n### Features of Contoso SmartView Glasses\n\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: These glasses feature an augmented reality interface that allows users to overlay digital information seamlessly in their real-world view.\n\n2. **Voice-Controlled AI Agent**: The product comes with a voice-controlled AI agent that enables hands-free operation and interaction with various functionalities.\n\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Users can capture high-definition videos with integrated 3D audio, enhancing the multimedia experience and providing immersive content creation capabilities.\n\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: The eyewear includes UV protection and blue light filtering, making it suitable for prolonged use by protecting the user’s eyes from harmful radiation and reducing strain.\n\n5. **Wireless Charging with Extended Battery Life**: Contoso ensures convenience and efficiency through wireless charging options along with an extended battery lifespan to keep the device operational longer.\n\n### Additional Information\n\n- **Sizing and Fit**: Guidelines are provided to help users find their perfect fit and make necessary style adjustments.\n- **Proper Care and Maintenance**: Instructions on cleaning and maintaining the SmartView Glasses are available to ensure longevity.\n- **Safety Tips**: Safety guidelines are detailed for using the glasses in both public and private settings.\n- **Troubleshooting**: Solutions for common issues are provided to assist users in resolving any difficulties.\n\n### Warranty and Policies\n\n- **Two-year Limited Warranty**: There is a two-year warranty on all electronic components of the product.\n- **Return Policy**: Contoso offers a 30-day return policy with no questions asked.\n- **Customer Support**: Users can reach out for assistance at support@contoso-galaxy-innovations.com.","logprobs":[]}

