data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":407,"item_id":"msg_98266cbfb57f837f00693a04ee3b28819091d5ba4ac53f3387","output_index":1,"content_index":0,"text":"Contoso's Smart Eyewear, specifically the SmartView Glasses, offers an array of advanced features designed for convenience and enhanced user experience. Here's a detailed overview:\n\n### Features of Contoso SmartView Glasses\n\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: The eyewear features an augmented reality interface that overlays digital information onto the user's real-world view, creating a seamless blend of both digital and reality.\n\n2. **Voice-Controlled AI Agent**: Equipped with a voice-controlled AI agent, the glasses allow for hands-free operation and interaction with various functionalities, making it user-friendly and accessible.\n\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: The glasses come with the capability of capturing high-definition videos complemented by integrated 3D audio, enhancing multimedia experiences and enabling immersive content creation.\n\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: Essential for prolonged use, the Smart Eyewear includes UV protection and blue light filters to reduce eye strain and protect against harmful radiation.\n\n5. **Wireless Charging with Extended Battery Life**: They offer wireless charging options along with an extended battery life to keep users connected and operational for extended periods.\n\n### User Guide Highlights\n\n- **Sizing and Fit**: Guidelines are provided to assist in finding the perfect fit and making necessary style adjustments.\n- **Proper Care and Maintenance**: Instructions on cleaning and caring for the glasses are available to ensure they remain in good condition.\n- **Break-in Period**: Guidance for users as they adjust to the augmented reality experience.\n- **Safety Tips**: Safety guidelines for using the glasses in different environments are outlined clearly.\n\n### Warranty and Policies\n\n- **Two-year Limited Warranty**: Contoso provides a two-year limited warranty on all electronic components of the product.\n- **Return Policy**: There is a 30-day return policy with no questions asked.\n- **Customer Support**: For assistance, users can contact support at support@contoso-galaxy-innovations.com.","logprobs":[]}

